1604235600.title: Inside Politics
1604235600.descr: Inside Politics is a political talk show, broadcast on CNN and anchored by CNN Chief National Correspondent John King. It features the most important political stories presented by a panel of well-sourced reporters. John King is an experienced reporter who covers the White House, Congress and the campaign trail, and interviews presidents, politicians and voters.

1604239200.title: U.S. State of the Union Address
1604239200.descr: Jake Tapper brings together major news makers, analysts and experts to tackle pressing domestic issues and diplomacy on the global stage.

1604242800.title: Fareed Zakaria GPS
1604242800.descr: Fareed Zakaria GPS is a weekly public affairs show hosted by an American journalist, political scientist, and author Fareed Zakaria. The "GPS" in the show's title stands for "Global Public Square," a reference to the show's focus on international issues and foreign affairs.

1604246400.title: Reliable Sources
1604246400.descr: Reliable Sources is a CNN Sunday morning talk show focused on analysis of the American news media, hosted by Brian Stelter. The media world is thoroughly examined and the news stories of the previous week are covered. The talk show highlights news about news and tells story behind the story, and features one-on-one interviews with journalists taking part in a news event.
